data.description: BONUS-SELLER TO GIVE 1 YEAR HOME WARRANTY WITH PURCHASE ($650 VALUE). Quaint Coastal home on 2 large lots just minutes from Perdido Bay with 2 driveways and ample space to park an RV and Boat.  As you enter, this home, you are greeted by vaulted ceilings and an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen and living area that leads to a large back deck. The well-appointed kitchen has been updated with new flooring, cabinets, and countertops and is equipped with modern appliances, providing a functional space for culinary enthusiasts. The primary suite is a private oasis, with an en-suite with double vanity and walk in shower providing a tranquil retreat. 2 Additional bedrooms are generously sized, offering versatility for guests or a home office. The 2-car garage has a workshop area  and also houses a separate living space for guests. The property has a private fenced yard and provides plenty of room for outdoor activities and entertaining. It is located in the highly desired, safe, pet friendly, beach neighborhood of Spanish Cove, a coastal paradise gracing the shores of Perdido Bay, just 5 minutes from the Lillian boat launch and only 15 minutes from the sugar white beaches of the Gulf of Mexico. There is something for everyone in this exclusive coastal golf cart community that sits on the Alabama/Florida line. Owners enjoy membership with a lifestyle full of amenities and remarkably affordable POA Dues of only $74/Mo (dues paid quarterly) and includes trash pick-up, 24 hours security, and key FOB entry into all facilities.  There are two clubhouses and a year-round junior Olympic sized swimming pool that is heated and covered in the winter months and this community also includes many sources of activities. If you like to relax, you can spend the day at the Spanish Cove beach, fish from the 500-ft pier, or watch the sunset while taking a stroll around this lovely community in your golf cart. This is coastal living at its finest. This home is a must see.
